<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 18:09:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>为什么中国、俄罗斯、伊朗和以色列政府在拜登辩论失败后幸灾乐祸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/why-china-russia-iran-and-israels-government-are-gloating-after-bidens-debate-debacle/00000190-73d7-d129-afba-fff7ac9c0000</link><description>敌人欢欣鼓舞，盟友焦虑：全球对乔·拜登表现和连任机会的大量报道反映了 11 月选举的巨大利害关系 — — 从美利坚共和国的未来到世界秩序本身</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 18:02:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/why-china-russia-iran-and-israels-government-are-gloating-after-bidens-debate-debacle/00000190-73d7-d129-afba-fff7ac9c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部长声称推翻大屠杀纪念馆主席的背后有“很多原因”，但没有引用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-says-many-reasons-to-oust-yad-vashem-chair-but-doesnt-cite-them/00000190-7442-d7a4-a9dc-ff7b631d0000</link><description>一份信息自由请求显示，约夫·基什部长的办公室只收到一封投诉信，其中没有像部长所声称的那样提出不当行为或虐待行为。该投诉是由一家美国组织在 Yad Vashem 因纠纷与该组织断绝关系后发出的</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 17:28:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-says-many-reasons-to-oust-yad-vashem-chair-but-doesnt-cite-them/00000190-7442-d7a4-a9dc-ff7b631d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 270 天：真主党副领袖称加沙休战是实现停火的唯一途径</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-270-hezbollah-deputy-chief-says-gaza-truce-only-path-to-cease-fire/00000190-745b-de25-a3df-7cfb14400000</link><description>据《纽约时报》报道，以色列国防军高级将领寻求在加沙停火，即使这会让哈马斯暂时掌权。 ■ 10 月 7 日被杀和绑架的以色列国防军观察员的父母发誓，将继续战斗，直到针对大屠杀事件成立国家调查委员会 ■ 内塔尼亚胡政府选择法官接替前首席大法官阿哈伦·巴拉克 (Aharon Barak) 在国际法院代表政府 ■ 战争结束 270 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:55:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-270-hezbollah-deputy-chief-says-gaza-truce-only-path-to-cease-fire/00000190-745b-de25-a3df-7cfb14400000</guid></item><item><title>以色列真的想被指控在加沙犯下更多战争罪吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-02/ty-article/.highlight/does-israel-actually-want-to-be-accused-of-more-war-crimes-in-gaza/00000190-73d7-dbfd-a5d1-f3d7f1ab0000</link><description>在看起来像是犯罪意图的竞争中，以色列政治人物坚持提倡折磨巴勒斯坦平民的政策，似乎是为了证明他们违反国际法的承诺</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:38:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-02/ty-article/.highlight/does-israel-actually-want-to-be-accused-of-more-war-crimes-in-gaza/00000190-73d7-dbfd-a5d1-f3d7f1ab0000</guid></item><item><title>“是时候再给和平一次机会了”：数千人聚集在特拉维夫参加以色列-巴勒斯坦和平会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-time-to-give-peace-another-chance-thousands-gather-at-peace-conference-in-tel-aviv/00000190-73b5-d705-a7f5-fbff44db0000</link><description>在一场题为“是时候了：伟大的和平会议”的活动中，在以色列人和巴勒斯坦人最黑暗的时期，竞技场上充满了对未来的希望。一位巴勒斯坦发言者说，“这个家园正在流血，如果我们现在不阻止，我们都会走上集体自杀的道路”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:33:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-time-to-give-peace-another-chance-thousands-gather-at-peace-conference-in-tel-aviv/00000190-73b5-d705-a7f5-fbff44db0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔和警方未能遏制以色列阿拉伯社区的犯罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-and-police-are-failing-to-stifle-crime-in-israels-arab-communities/00000190-73b4-d705-a7f5-fbfff7890000</link><description>6 月份，以色列阿拉伯社区发生了 23 起凶杀案，使年度总数达到 109 起 ■ 在国家安全部长 Itamar Ben-Gvir 的领导下，阿拉伯社区的谋杀案数量增加了一倍</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:31:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-and-police-are-failing-to-stifle-crime-in-israels-arab-communities/00000190-73b4-d705-a7f5-fbfff7890000</guid></item><item><title>纽约时报：即使哈马斯掌权，以色列陆军领导人仍希望加沙停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/nyt-reports-that-israeli-army-brass-want-cease-fire-in-gaza-even-with-hamas-intact/00000190-7390-d0bf-a9fd-77fa3a0a0000</link><description>据《纽约时报》报道，以色列国防军官员正在推动结束加沙战争，认为这是解救人质并缓和与真主党关系的唯一机会。内塔尼亚胡反驳说，他不知道消息来源是谁，但这种情况“不会发生”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 14:12:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/nyt-reports-that-israeli-army-brass-want-cease-fire-in-gaza-even-with-hamas-intact/00000190-7390-d0bf-a9fd-77fa3a0a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会将于7月底休会三个月，招致人质亲属批评</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/knesset-to-go-on-three-month-recess-drawing-criticism-from-hostages-relatives/00000190-7341-d0bf-a9fd-77fb7ba30000</link><description>民族联盟党提交了一项取消休会的法案，预计这将是有史以来最长的一次休会，但需要联盟的合作才能推进。亲戚们说：“只要达成协议，送回 120 名人质，你就能得到你想要的假期。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 13:21:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/knesset-to-go-on-three-month-recess-drawing-criticism-from-hostages-relatives/00000190-7341-d0bf-a9fd-77fb7ba30000</guid></item><item><title>希西家王什么时候统治？有争议的文物可能会解决圣经争议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-07-02/ty-article/when-did-king-hezekiah-reign-controversial-artifacts-may-resolve-biblical-controversy/00000190-7334-d084-a7dc-fbb7cbb10000</link><description>《圣经》对于犹大王在位期间反抗亚述的说法是自相矛盾的。对古物市场印章的研究声称可以打破僵局</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 12:05:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-07-02/ty-article/when-did-king-hezekiah-reign-controversial-artifacts-may-resolve-biblical-controversy/00000190-7334-d084-a7dc-fbb7cbb10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，两名以色列士兵在加沙中部战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-central-gaza-combat-idf-says/00000190-72fb-d084-a7dc-faffbbad0000</link><description>30岁，军士长。来自耶路撒冷的 Nadav Elchanan Knoller（解析）和 25 岁的 Eyal Avnion 少校是周一遇难的两名士兵。另一名士兵在战斗中受伤</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 11:35:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-central-gaza-combat-idf-says/00000190-72fb-d084-a7dc-faffbbad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列承诺建立将生病的加沙人经埃及转移到国外接受治疗的系统</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-pledges-to-establish-system-to-transfer-sick-gazans-for-medical-treatment-abroad/00000190-72d1-dbfd-a5d1-f2d338b60000</link><description>以色列表示将在一周内通报该计划的最新进展。由于右翼抗议，请愿者的律师被迫在看守下离开高等法院听证会</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 11:26:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-pledges-to-establish-system-to-transfer-sick-gazans-for-medical-treatment-abroad/00000190-72d1-dbfd-a5d1-f2d338b60000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争将如何改变以色列的心理治疗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/borderline-nationality-disorder-should-israeli-psychotherapy-mind-the-gaza-war/00000190-6988-dda7-a9d0-69fe80d60000</link><description>弗洛伊德和他的弟子们尽最大努力不让政治现实渗透到他们与患者的谈话中，这一决定几乎导致了他们的运动的结束</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 10:23:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/borderline-nationality-disorder-should-israeli-psychotherapy-mind-the-gaza-war/00000190-6988-dda7-a9d0-69fe80d60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人行横道杀手被判16年监禁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/murdered-of-israeli-pedestrian-at-a-crosswalk-sentenced-for-16-years-in-prison/00000190-7277-d129-afba-fff7119a0000</link><description>阿迪·米兹拉希 (Adi Mizrahi) 于 2022 年在霍隆刺伤了 52 岁的尤里·沃尔科夫 (Yuri Volkov)，在认罪协议中因冷漠而被指控犯有谋杀罪。起诉书称，证据表明很难确定沃尔科夫的死亡是由刺伤还是他接受的医疗造成的</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 09:44:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/murdered-of-israeli-pedestrian-at-a-crosswalk-sentenced-for-16-years-in-prison/00000190-7277-d129-afba-fff7119a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列为加沙海水淡化厂和污水处理厂重新通电</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-provides-gaza-with-electricity-to-run-water-desalination-and-sewage-plant/00000190-728d-d084-a7dc-fa8fca530000</link><description>以色列安全官员表示，修复加沙电线并将其连接到以色列电网是一项人道主义努力，旨在防止加沙爆发疾病和污染，这些疾病可能危及加沙地带的以色列国防军部队和以色列居民</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 09:12:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-provides-gaza-with-electricity-to-run-water-desalination-and-sewage-plant/00000190-728d-d084-a7dc-fa8fca530000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家检察官：称阿拉伯联合名单党议员为恐怖分子构成言论保护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/state-prosecutor-calling-arab-lawmakers-terrorists-constitutes-protected-speech/00000190-7216-d0bf-a9fd-76fe366f0000</link><description>该声明是为了回应 UAL 议员 Waleed Alhwashla 要求取消国家宣教部长 Orit Strock 的豁免权，以便以煽动罪对她提出起诉，此前她在 5 月份称该党为“穿着西装、打领带、笑容甜美的恐怖分子”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 08:25:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/state-prosecutor-calling-arab-lawmakers-terrorists-constitutes-protected-speech/00000190-7216-d0bf-a9fd-76fe366f0000</guid></item><item><title>反对党领袖拉皮德称内塔尼亚胡计划解雇以色列总检察长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/opposition-leader-lapid-says-netanyahu-planning-to-fire-israels-ag/00000190-720d-d129-afba-ffffb6570000</link><description>极右翼部长大卫·阿姆萨勒姆指责司法部长“竭尽全力推翻政府”。拉皮德警告内塔尼亚胡正在考虑解雇总检察长，并告诉他的政党的立法者，不排除任何选择，包括集体辞职</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 08:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/opposition-leader-lapid-says-netanyahu-planning-to-fire-israels-ag/00000190-720d-d129-afba-ffffb6570000</guid></item><item><title>以色列如何应对勒庞领导的全国集会党可能赢得的极右翼法国大选</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/how-israel-is-contending-with-a-potential-far-right-french-election-win-by-le-pens-party/00000190-6fe7-dbfd-a5d1-eff783700000</link><description>以色列现在需要权衡法国极右翼目前对以色列的立场、其反犹太主义根源以及法国犹太社区对其民族主义言论的恐惧，因为几十年来一直拒绝与法国极右翼建立任何官方关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 03:05:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/how-israel-is-contending-with-a-potential-far-right-french-election-win-by-le-pens-party/00000190-6fe7-dbfd-a5d1-eff783700000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队准备结束加沙战斗，但未达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-set-to-wind-down-fighting-in-gaza-but-without-reaching-a-hostage-deal/00000190-6f9a-d0bf-a9fd-6ffa14f20000</link><description>关键问题将是如何让公众相信以色列已经实现了战争期间的目标，尽管哈马斯尚未被彻底击败，而且 120 名人质仍滞留在加沙。 ■ 以色列领导人对 Al-Shifa 获释一事进行指责医院院长，内塔尼亚胡时代的惨败象征</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 03:05:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-set-to-wind-down-fighting-in-gaza-but-without-reaching-a-hostage-deal/00000190-6f9a-d0bf-a9fd-6ffa14f20000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射了 15 枚火箭弹，其中一些在边境城镇附近引发火灾</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article-live/netanyahu-says-israel-close-to-eliminating-hamas-military/00000190-713b-d33f-a7b9-75bfb46f0000</link><description>纽约时报：以色列国防军高级将领希望停火；内塔尼亚胡：这并没有发生 ■ 两名以色列士兵在加沙中部的战斗中丧生 ■ 内塔尼亚胡办公室表示，政府不知道释放 Al-Shifa 医院院长的决定 ■ 以色列为加沙海水淡化和污水处理厂重新通电 ■ Ben-格维尔呼吁辛贝特酋长辞职 ■ 据以色列国防军报道，火箭袭击加沙边境社区后，以色列军队连夜袭击了一些地点</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 02:25:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article-live/netanyahu-says-israel-close-to-eliminating-hamas-military/00000190-713b-d33f-a7b9-75bfb46f0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院以色列新法官抨击种族灭绝听证会“在思想上不诚实”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-judge-at-icj-slammed-genocide-hearing-as-intellectually-dishonest/00000190-7027-d33f-a7b9-74b7be7f0000</link><description>佩雷斯学术中心院长罗恩·夏皮拉教授被吹捧为现任政府可能任命的最高法院法官，政府希望任命一名保守派法官</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 21:31:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-judge-at-icj-slammed-genocide-hearing-as-intellectually-dishonest/00000190-7027-d33f-a7b9-74b7be7f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>